data.title: 9 most famous neoclassical paintings
data.meta_description: Neoclassical art revives the elegance of ancient Greece and Rome, focusing on balanced compositions and idealized beauty. This 18th-century movement, led by artists like Jacques-Louis David, emphasizes historical themes and classical ideals.
